            "title": "太子大南街唐樓起火 消防升雲梯灌救 住戶落街暫避",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/42d0d7a051eaee133ea5212df773d0a5/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250312/_2025031222111066349.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>今日（12日）晚上8時許，太子大南街134至140A號一唐樓單位發生火警，現場一度傳出爆炸聲，多人報警求助。10多名住戶自行疏散落樓，消防出動一條喉及一隊煙帽隊，並架起雲梯灌救，迅速將火救熄，起火原因有待調查，事件中無人受傷。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4133774/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"消防出動一條喉及一隊煙帽隊灌救。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b06e347b0c26988b573c90925fd8a997/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250312_220524103_10.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        消防出動一條喉及一隊煙帽隊灌救。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4133775/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"消防架起雲梯灌救。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/681b86780d2205e10df5b5d5eecdefa8/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250312_220524103_09.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n       