        {
            "title": "有片｜東涌逸東邨巴士起火 消防開喉灌救引途人圍觀",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<div id=\"vdo-player-container\">\n<video class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin\" controls=\"\" id=\"vdo-player\" muted=\"\" playsinline=\"\" poster=\"\" width=\"100%\">\n<source src=\"https://video.hkhl.hk/90968566ff4271efb1a95014c1ca0102/5538bf41bf524150b8b4c0796bd314c8-270f36a2efaae14b0b581431c503d809-ld.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                        Your browser does not support the video tag.\n                    </source></video>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container web\" data-vslot=\"vod_ad\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67d1873f7f11a\"></div>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container mweb\" data-vslot0=\"vod_ad,2\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67d1873f7f11e\"></div>\n</div>\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/30e368e90eddcb7676e433acb989908f/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250312/_2025031221052945483.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>東涌有巴士起火。今日（12日）晚上7時許，一輛空載的龍運雙層巴士於逸東邨居逸樓對開的巴士總站起火，車長發現後立即報警，消防到場開喉灌救將火救熄，意外中無人受傷，起火原因有待調查。\n\n</p>\n<p>根據網上圖片所見，巴士車尾位置首先起火，火勢相當猛烈，冒出大量濃煙，引來多名市民圍觀。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4133698/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"巴士車尾起火，冒出大量濃煙。fb「是日快快-巴士即日相」圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/44b1209cb8e76cf2eea49132f78ba484/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250312_201416558.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        巴士車尾起火，冒出大量濃煙。fb「是日快快-巴士即日相」圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4133702/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"火警引來多名居民圍觀。網上片段截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/dbb377ddf86e7bf294868cbb1faee4bd/2025-03/3_6.PNG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        火警引來多名居民圍觀。網上片段截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4133703/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"消防開喉將火救熄。網上片段截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/988cb73b10aaefa90fa5e49fa7b39061/2025-03/1_9.PNG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        消防開喉將火救熄。網上片段截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4133696/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"消防開喉將火救熄。梁國鋒攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0652ae126389a802ff80ab8ed12f5399/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250312_202137988_05.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        消防開喉將火救熄。梁國鋒攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4133697/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"消防開喉將火救熄。梁國鋒攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ebd52a2097ddb16ad4a07c55b4730b25/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250312_202137988_08.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        消防開喉將火救熄。梁國鋒攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4133694/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"現場為逸東邨居逸樓對開。梁國鋒攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cbf3a64fd1fbc4ed19da724ab31af636/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250312_202137988_02_1_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        現場為逸東邨居逸樓對開。梁國鋒攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4133695/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"消防開喉將火救熄。梁國鋒攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f0624d5794bfbb04347e9b891d5dd35a/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250312_202137988_06_1_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n  